Mr. Agrawal has wide-ranging experience in strategy and capital markets and has helped various large Indian and global corporates raise over US$10 billion from the capital markets. In his advisory capacity, Mr. Agrawal has advised several business groups like Tatas, AV Birla, GMR, ICICI, Bharti, DLF, etc.

